  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid, with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> chicken thigh fillets</strong> and cook for 3-4 min, turning once half way, until they're golden on both sides</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong> to a bowl, cover them with 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and leave them to soak</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice&nbsp;the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>tomatoes</strong>&nbsp;into wedges</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> are golden, transfer them to a plate, leaving any juices behind&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min over a medium-low heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> tomato paste</strong>,<strong> tomato wedges</strong>, <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong> (including the soaking liquid), half of the<strong> balsamic vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min</p>\r\n<p>Return the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to the pan, cover with a lid and cook for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p>\r\n<p>Re-boil a kettle&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1097.-step-4-x400.jpg",
